  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流程图，功能是找出正整数n的所有约数。用户输入n，然后程序逐个检查1到n之间的每个数是否能整除n。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "START",
        "ReadN",
        "n"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，这是一个约数查找算法。我先用圆角矩形画START节点，然后接一个平行四边形的ReadN来读取输入，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "START",
        "ReadN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，ReadN之后需要初始化一个计数器i=1，用矩形表示赋值操作。然后进入一个循环，判断i是否小于等于n。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Assign",
        "i",
        "Loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了Assign节点设置i=1，然后用菱形画Loop判断节点，标注条件\"i <= n\"。这个菱形应该有两个出口吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Assign",
        "Loop",
        "i <= n"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，Loop为False的时候直接结束程序，为True的时候继续检查n能否被i整除。所以False分支要连到End节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Loop",
        "False",
        "End"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加End节点，用双圆角矩形表示终止。现在Loop的True分支需要连到下一个判断，检查n % i == 0，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Loop",
        "True",
        "Check",
        "n % i == 0"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，这个Check节点也是菱形，判断当前i是否是n的约数。如果是，就打印i；如果不是，就跳过打印直接增加i的值。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Check",
        "Print",
        "Increment"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我画好了Check节点，从它分出两条线：True分支连到Print节点，用平行四边形表示输出；False分支连到Increment。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Check",
        "True",
        "False",
        "Print",
        "Increment"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Print节点要标注\"Print i\"，显示当前找到的约数。Increment节点是i = i + 1，然后要回到Loop重新判断，形成循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Print",
        "Increment",
        "Loop",
        "i = i + 1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，Print之后也要先到Increment，然后Increment再连回Loop。这样无论是否找到约数，i都会递增继续下一轮。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Print",
        "Increment",
        "Loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。让我看看整体结构——START、ReadN、Assign、Loop，然后Loop分出False到End，True到Check。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "START",
        "ReadN",
        "Assign",
        "Loop",
        "End",
        "Check"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我确认一下流向：Check的True走Print然后Increment，Check的False直接走Increment，两条路汇合后都回到Loop。这样逻辑对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Check",
        "True",
        "False",
        "Print",
        "Increment",
        "Loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但有个细节——Print输出之后也是要到Increment的，不是直接回Loop。你刚才说的\"Print然后Increment\"是对的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Print",
