      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "啊，我刚才画的时候把Print直接连回Loop了，漏掉了Increment。我修正一下：Print必须先到Increment[i = i + 1]，然后再回Loop。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Print",
